</rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="b" cause="deletion">Mechanicae:
(1)  eadem semper manet potentia <note type="editorial">|</note> <del>seu vis</del> <note type="editorial"><hi rendition="#i">gestr.</hi> |</note> (2) eadem semper manet <app><rdg wit="#L" n="aa">directio </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="bb">determin </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="cc">directio. </rdg></app></rdg></app></rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="2"> Propositio <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg></app>
fundamentalis totius scientiae
