patientibus, eadem semper manet potentia<index indexName="Sachen"><term>potentia</term></index> et directio<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio</term></index> totius aggregati.<index indexName="Sachen"><term>potentia totius aggregati</term></index><index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio totius aggregati</term></index>
<hi rendition="#g">Potentia</hi><index indexName="Sachen"><term>potentia</term></index> est quantitas
effectus,<index indexName="Sachen"><term>quantitas effectus</term></index> quem res aliqua producere potest. Directio<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio</term></index> est linea motus,<index indexName="Sachen"><term>linea motus</term></index> vel si curva sit ejus tangens;
directio totius
aggregati<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio totius aggregati</term></index> eadem est quae directio centri gravitatis.<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio centri gravitatis</term></index><index indexName="Sachen"><term>centrum gravitatis</term></index> Nulla enim alia totius directio<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio</term></index> intelligi potest.
In aggregato corporum quotcunque sibi relicto<index indexName="Sachen"><term>aggregatum corporum sibi relictum</term></index> eadem semper potentia et
<app type="Bfootnote"><lem type="main">directio totius</lem><note type="lemma-abbrev">directio</note><rdg wit="#L" n="1"> conservatur </rdg><rdg wit="#L" n="2"> totius <hi rendition="#i">L</hi></rdg></app>
aggregati<index indexName="Sachen"><term>potentia totius aggregati</term></index><index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio totius aggregati</term></index> servatur. Cum enim sibi relictum esse intelligamus, nihil est quod mutet. Servatur ergo potentia<index indexName="Sachen"><term>potentia</term></index> et
directio<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio</term></index> non quidem partium,<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio partium</term></index><index indexName="Sachen"><term>potentia partium</term></index> eae enim invicem patiuntur, augentque et minuunt potentiam, et mutant
directionem; sed totius. Est autem directio totius<index indexName="Sachen"><term>directio totius</term></index> eadem quae directio certi alicujus puncti. Quod semper
progredi necesse est.</p><figure rendition="#own-line_centered" xml:id="Ch41.p7"><graphic url="../gesamttex/edit_VIII,3/images/LH_37_05_162r_d1.svg" width="238.491pt" xml:id="Ch41.p7.g1"/><head rendition="#c">[<hi rendition="#i">Fig. 1</hi>]</head></figure><p xml:id="Ch41.p8">Sit corpus <hi rendition="#i">A</hi>, ejus celeritas <formula xml:id="Ch41.p8.m1"><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mpadded width="+1.7pt"><m:mi>a</m:mi></m:mpadded><m:mo rspace="4.2pt">⊓</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>⁢</m:mo><m:mi>D</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></formula>[,] corpus <hi rendition="#i">B</hi>, ejus celeritas <formula xml:id="Ch41.p8.m2"><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mpadded width="+1.7pt"><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:mpadded><m:mo rspace="4.2pt">⊓</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mi>D</m:mi><m:mo>⁢</m:mo><m:mi>E</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></formula>[,] distantia corporum <formula xml:id="Ch41.p8.m3"><m:math xmlns:m="http://www.w3.org/1998/Math/MathML" display="inline"><m:mrow><m:mrow><m:mi>a</m:mi><m:mo>+</m:mo><m:mpadded width="+1.7pt"><m:mi>b</m:mi></m:mpadded></m:mrow><m:mo rspace="7.5pt">⊓</m:mo><m:mrow><m:mi>C</m:mi><m:mo>⁢</m:mo><m:mi>E</m:mi></m:mrow></m:mrow></m:math></formula>, punctum concursus<index indexName="Sachen"><term>punctum concursus</term></index> <hi rendition="#i">D</hi>. Sit centrum gravitatis<index indexName="Sachen"><term>centrum gravitatis</term></index>
